HEADWORD: Unseminared
<hw>Un*sem"i*nared</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See 1st
<er>Un-</er>, and <er>Semen</er>.]</ety> <def>Deprived of virility, or
